      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1 used under DePuy Synthes quality management system (ISO 13485 certified). Input deck version control maintained in Git repository with tagged releases. Regression test suite of 42 benchmark cases executed and passed prior to study runs. SQA documentation package available in design history file."
